      "writtenOn": "2015-11-30T17:59:37Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Unfortunately, LANDSCAPE is by definition 270 degrees clockwise, and I think ordering by increasing degrees is more desirable. There\u0027s really no canonical order with the labels.\n\nDo you suggest we translate clockwise degrees to counterclockwise degrees as we read the skins? I think it would get confusing to have to deal with clockwise and counterclockwise degrees.",
      "parentUuid": "5bda4b65_8ec5db61",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 66,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 69,
        "endChar": 54
      },
      "revId": "1d535b3a9fae1e730823a5d644a71e3043d073e3",
