      "writtenOn": "2015-11-30T18:21:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Can you point me towards that definition? I agree that increasing degrees is more desirable.\n\nThe most important thing is (as much as possible) consistency across our entire codebase AND the skin file format.",
      "parentUuid": "1bea93c4_c233e636",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 66,
